OL,7,FA victim of the infected blood scandal
OL,8,Ffrom Northern Ireland has described
OL,9,Fthe wait for compensation as "torture".
OL,11,FNigel Hamilton, from Co Antrim, was
OL,12,Fgiving evidence as the Infected Blood
OL,13,FInquiry reopened on Wednesday to
OL,14,Fexamine concerns about compensation.
OL,16,FThe special hearing around the
OL,17,Ftreatment disaster heard that some
OL,18,Fpeople are dying before receiving
OL,19,Fpayments.
