OL,7,FMr Hamilton said: "We need justice,
OL,8,Fwe're entitled to justice, and we will
OL,9,Fhave justice."
OL,11,FSome victims of the infected blood
OL,12,Fscandal will die before they receive
OL,13,Fcompensation and the current number of
OL,14,Fpeople who have received a payout is
OL,15,F"unsatisfactory", the Government has
OL,16,Fadmitted.
