OL,7,FPeople affected by the scandal, dubbed
OL,8,Fthe "biggest disaster in the history
OL,9,Fof the NHS", said they "don't have
OL,10,Ftime on our side" as they urged
OL,11,Fofficials to speed up compensation
OL,12,Fpayments.
OL,14,FSir Brian Langstaff, chairman of the
OL,15,FInfected Blood Inquiry, is holding two
OL,16,Fdays of special hearings to examine
OL,17,Fthe "timeliness and adequacy of the
OL,18,FGovernment's response to compensation".
