OL,7,FOpening the hearing, Sir Brian said:
OL,8,F"It is no secret that the inquiry has
OL,9,Freceived letter after letter, email
OL,10,Fafter email, call after call,
OL,11,Fexpressing worries and concerns about
OL,12,Fhow compensation is being delivered.
OL,14,F"The inquiry will do everything in its
OL,15,Fpower to identify action that can be
OL,16,Ftaken by the Government and by the
OL,17,FInfected Blood Compensation Authority
OL,18,Fto improve the delivery of
OL,19,Fcompensation and to ensure that
OL,20,Fjustice is done."
