OL,7,FCabinet Office minister Nick
OL,8,FThomas`Symonds began his evidence by
OL,9,Fapologising to victims.
OL,11,F"I know many people before me will
OL,12,Fhave suffered unimaginably because of
OL,13,Fthis scandal, I would like to
OL,14,Facknowledge that the government has
OL,15,Ffailed you over decades on behalf of
OL,16,Fthe state. I am sorry," he said.
