OL,7,FPointing out that it could be years
OL,8,Fbefore some people will receive
OL,9,Fcompensation, inquiry counsel Jenni
OL,10,FRichards KC asked Mr Thomas`Symonds
OL,11,Fwhether both infected and affected
OL,12,Fpeople will die before they receive
OL,13,Fcompensation.
OL,15,F"Yes," he replied.
OL,17,FThe minister, who was heckled as he
OL,18,Fgave evidence, told the hearing that
OL,19,Fhe is "restless for further progress
OL,20,Fon payments".
