OL,7,FMs Richards read out the latest
OL,8,Fcompensation figures from the IBCA,
OL,9,Fwhich show that just over 100 people
OL,10,Fhave received a payment, saying:
OL,11,F"That's a profoundly unsatisfactory
OL,12,Fstate of affairs, isn't it?"
OL,14,FMr Thomas`Symonds replied: "It
OL,15,Fabsolutely is, and I'm never going to
OL,16,Fthink this is satisfactory until
OL,17,Feverybody has received the
OL,18,Fcompensation they are due."
