OL,7,FThe grandmother gave up teaching in
OL,8,F1991 to look after her husband, John,
OL,9,Fwho contracted HIV and hepatitis C
OL,10,Fwhile receiving treatment for
OL,11,Fhaemophilia and who died from Aids in
OL,12,F1994 at the age of 41.
OL,14,FMore than 30,000 people in the UK were
OL,15,Finfected with HIV and hepatitis C
